## Next Step: Manual Upload
The release IPA has been successfully built at:
`build/ios/ipa/roze.ipa`

To complete the release:
1.  **Open Transporter**: Open the "Transporter" app on your Mac.
2.  **Add IPA**: Drag and drop the file from [build/ios/ipa/roze.ipa](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/build/ios/ipa/roze.ipa) into Transporter.
3.  **Deliver**: Click **Deliver** to upload it to App Store Connect.
4.  **Wait**: Once it's "Processing" in App Store Connect, you can submit the version for review.

> [!NOTE]
> If you notice the version number is still `1.0.0` in App Store Connect, you may need to update it manually in the **General** tab of the **Runner** target in Xcode, as it seems to be hardcoded there.
